<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>
      Subscription Plan Request Received - Our Team Will Reach Out Soon
    </title>
    <style>
      /* Inline CSS styles for email compatibility */
      .container {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 600px;
        /* Maximum width of the container */
        margin: auto;
        /* Center the container */
      }

      .instruction-box {
        border: 2px solid #df7b01;
        /* Orange border */
        border-radius: 8px;
        /* Rounded corners */
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        /* Light gray background */
        margin: 20px 0;
        /* Space around the box */
      }

      .instruction-box p {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        /* Space between paragraphs */
        line-height: 1.6;
        /* Increase line height for readability */
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        background-color: #df7b01;
        /* Orange background */
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        /* Rounded corners */
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
        /* Center text inside button */
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 style="text-align: center">
        Subscription Plan Request Received – Our Team Will Reach Out Soon
      </h1>
      <div class="instruction-box">
        <p>
          Dear <%= name %>, <br /><br />
          Thank you for submitting your subscription plan request for our
          corporate services. We’re excited to partner with you and help meet
          your business needs.<br /><br />
          Our team is currently reviewing your request, and one of our
          representatives will reach out to you shortly with more details. If
          you have any immediate questions, please feel free to reply to this
          email.

          <br />
          <br />
          <br />
          Thank you, <br />
          The BuzzBreach Team
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
